<p>The vertical barrel is a decoration. It can be crafted at the <a href="../../source/buildings/sawmill">Sawmill</a>.
<br /></p>

<h2 id="using-the-vertical-barrel">Using the Vertical Barrel</h2>

<p>Vertical barrels are decorations and have no purpose. They are often used in the <a href="../../source/buildings/tavern">Tavern</a> schematics.</p>
